videos.description: Cincinnati's Jeremiah Davenport misses the front end of a 1-and-1, and Wichita State takes it the other way but Alterique Gilbert just misses a triple which would have won it for the Shockers.
videos.headline: Cincinnati survives wild final sequence to advance to AAC final
